{"type": "article", "id": 56345, "title": "这款橱柜灵感源自《阴翳礼赞》，而且是纯手工制作｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-09-12T23:03:49Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 3875, "name": "包装设计"}, {"id": 52704, "name": "Hugh Miller Furniture"}, {"id": 7058, "name": "造作"}, {"id": 16335, "name": "Plumen"}, {"id": 2999, "name": "Aesop"}, {"id": 52705, "name": "Moët & Chandon"}, {"id": 18584, "name": "Virgil Abloh"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 130, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180913124829CrivcRXHgVmDQIj7.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; min-height: 13.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p class=\"\">「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。<br></p><h3>A Shadow-Inspired Drinks Cabinet by Hugh Miller Furniture</h3><p>Hugh Miller 是一位专门从事木材家具的设计和应用的英国艺术家，深受日本文化影响，我们曾介绍过一系列他设计的咖啡套装 The Coffee Ceremony。</p><p>最近，他又花费了大约 1000 个小时的手工制作时间，将在伦敦设计节期间推出首次亮相的 In Shadows 饮品橱柜，结合了日本竹子、实心黄铜棒和英国榆木等材料，经由墨水染色，呈现出阴影效果。收纳在柜中的物品，经由阴影和光线的过滤，也呈现出含蓄内敛的美感。</p><p>据称这款橱柜的名字，来源于日本作家谷崎润一郎的名作《阴翳礼赞》。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180913003726a4SQwG9OlR123yjA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.762500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180913003728QjpWGhRYsdZIXvm4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.663281\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180913003726jKVlsHSqNFJZ08nE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.516406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201809130037281sl4OaBtLZQFIwzM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.516406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180913003729wKvCejcXMNoLpfgb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.521094\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180913003729D5U4xhSFwABWnotd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180913003730FfUEbku0X2wx37cj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.455469\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.hughmillerfurniture.co.uk/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Hugh Miller Furniture</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>COSMO 星格™全屋高定系 by 造作</h3><p>历时三年研发, 家居设计品牌造作的 COSMO 星格™全屋高定系上线。用模块设计、大工业生产配合线上用户定制系统，第一次将用户作为主体引入空间定制过程，把空间设计的主导权交还给用户，用标准模块化组件，创造从玄关、书房、卧室到餐厅、客厅，皆可自由完成的“全屋自定制”系统。</p><p>据称，这个系列的灵感来源于宇宙星辰, 受此意象启发, 造作艺术总监、意大利设计师 Luca Nichetto 将星宇灵感化为精密设计，23 个格子单元，5 种连接件，如同星球和引力，组成万千变化的家的世界。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=g0785um5vgc\" allowfullscreen=\"“true”\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201809130038259de0ZLrWScbQsV3v.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.749618\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180913003825pQjTK6uXOiBh9cq8.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180913003825RDQmJdATr2bu0tn5.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180913003825D5kuKwY1hHr2748F.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180913003826HoNqtX8ecTkywbd1.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201809130038266y7WEmnGCfOQsqcL.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180913003826xHM5WVszNO3nZmce.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>001 LED by Plumen</h3><p>Plumen 公司来自伦敦，成立于 2010 年。由三名设计师 Nicolas Roope、Michael George Hemus 和 Ronnie Renton 共同创立，希望通过努力能创造出好看又实用的灯具。该公司曾经推出过一系列新概念的灯饰“Plumen 001”，也是世界上第一个设计师低能灯泡。</p><p>最近，它们又推出新品 001 LED 灯具，001 LED 是 Plumen 001 的更新版本，取代了之前的荧光技术，更加高效节能，更易控制调光，以及延长使用寿命，超过 2 万小时。</p><p>创意总监 Nicolas Roope 称 LED 版本有潜力成为新的经典。它仍然保留了原始的、识别度极高的双环形状。售价 49 美元起，<a href=\"https://usshop.plumen.com/collections/plumen-001-led/products/plumen-001-led\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180913003900A7h5349YvQOtRpNX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.300813\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180913003900QPd6mpRKhJx5B32s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.299492\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180913003900woxkycdJnYZpjmXL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.299492\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180913003901OCtfyVp9bkSmPjJz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.299492\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180913003900TdvJM6GbYkzRlrwV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.299492\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：Plumen</figcaption></figure></div><h3>A Brass Oil Burner by Henry Wilson for Aesop</h3><p>澳洲有机护肤品牌 Aesop，与悉尼工业设计师 Henry Wilson 合作，推出首款家居用品“黄铜燃油炉”，希望为家居空间中注入优雅和香气。</p><p>它采用古老的蜡铸工艺制成，重约 1 千克，具有不规则和不对称的形状，意在反映 Aesop 在美容护肤领域的天然有机理念。据 Designboom 报道，这款黄铜燃油炉将于本月晚些时候发布，零售价 195 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180913004018SW1BoT2VpnbFPY6K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180913004018EdMW1u3iTHvQms6B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.641880\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201809130040199ZhzA4PSI7JFG0Qd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.612500\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Limited Edition Moët &amp; Chandon Champagne Bottle by Virgil Abloh</h3><p>当红设计师 Virgil Abloh 与 LVMH 集团旗下香槟品牌 Moët &amp; Chandon 合作，推出限量版 Moët &amp; Chandon 香槟。这也是 Moët &amp; Chandon 有史以来的首个设计师合作项目。</p><p>目前在美国销量第一的 Moët 代表性 Nectar Imperial Rosé 香槟，成为这次合作的主角，Virgil 除了为这款香槟换上白色新装外，更将签名式的 “DO NOT DROP” 字样点缀于瓶身之上。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180913004042yHkcmYGB0Fq2ODtr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.622787\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180913004042iKOWR4f9mqkEpPoS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.536567\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180913004042Ib5Sog8zWYeB7yXV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.378063\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180913004042rKRugyM6tfPS4Dqo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}